OL,6,FThe 42-year-old was rushed to hospital
OL,7,Fin a critical condition where he was
OL,8,Fput on a life support machine and died
OL,9,Fnearly a month later on November 12
OL,10,F2021.
OL,12,FRiccardo's sister, Ramona Marsh, said:
OL,13,F"It's our way of getting some answers,
OL,14,Fto seek some justice for Riccardo and
OL,15,Fto also get some closure which we
OL,16,Fdesperately need."
OL,18,FA man was arrested following on from
OL,19,FRiccardo's death but has since been
OL,20,Freleased, with the Metropolitan Police
OL,21,Fsaying the case is discontinued.
