OL,3,CFamily of assault victim call for
OL,4,Cjustice three years on from death
OL,6,F"As his big sister, I've always been
OL,7,Fthere from when we were kids to look
OL,8,Fout for him and I just wasn't able to
OL,9,Fdo that for him this time," said Ms
OL,10,FMarsh.
OL,12,FRiccardo went on a night out, where he
OL,13,Fwas allegedly 'punched once to the
OL,14,Fhead' and 'fell back and broke his
OL,15,Fback in three places and fractured his
OL,16,Fskull'.
OL,18,FThe family feel that the police didn't
OL,19,Ftreat the incident as a homicide, and
OL,20,Fignored 'crucial' information from
OL,21,Fwitnesses.
