OL,3,CFamily of assault victim call for
OL,4,Cjustice three years on from death
OL,6,F"This is really upsetting for us," she
OL,7,Fcontinued.
OL,9,F"We feel that we need to do something
OL,10,Fourselves as a family because we're
OL,11,Fnot getting it anywhere else, so we're
OL,12,Fleft with no alternative but to seek
OL,13,Fjustice the best we can."
OL,15,FThe Met police told ITV News : "A
OL,16,Fthorough investigation was carried out
OL,17,Finto the circumstances surrounding the
OL,18,Fincident which led to Riccardo's death.
