OL,6,F"This included analysing CCTV and
OL,7,Fspeaking to those who were present and
OL,8,Fwitnessed the incident.
OL,10,F"All the evidence was presented to the
OL,11,FCrown Prosecution Service who decided
OL,12,Fthat the case should be discontinued."
OL,14,FThe money is being raised for legal
OL,15,Frepresentation when In November, a
OL,16,Fcoroner's court will decided whether
OL,17,FRiccardo's death was lawful or
OL,18,Funlawful.
